Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.24,0:00:09.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Any girl that goes to Altair either dies or transforms into a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.59,0:00:11.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that means Mix?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.47,0:00:14.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We found her, but it wasn't Mix anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.27,0:00:16.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She'd lost her memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.36,0:00:19.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are Zessica and Yunoha all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.80,0:00:21.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're all right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.81,0:00:24.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The checkups didn't find anything wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.92,0:00:28.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if we'd been there just a little longer...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.14,0:00:35.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did Mikono come back yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.21,0:00:38.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, she's still searching for High Commander Fudo.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.91,0:00:41.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How's Shrade?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.82,0:00:45.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's all right for now, but they don't know if it'll take.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.70,0:00:51.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So the High Commander is missing and Shrade's tapped out?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.34,0:00:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Neo-Deava is good as dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.90,0:00:55.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We might as well surrender now!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.47,0:00:59.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not over yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.67,0:01:03.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We should regroup and head back up to Altair!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.55,0:01:04.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Andy?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.59,0:01:07.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will save Mix.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.59,0:01:12.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Andy...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.76,0:01:15.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Andy! Are you okay?{damn it Amata}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.79,0:01:18.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.08,0:01:23.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not giving up. I'll get Mix back if it's the last thing I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{op}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.11,0:03:01.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was so close. I almost saw it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.08,0:03:07.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The perfect melody of love echoing between two worlds.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.41,0:03:11.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.05,0:03:15.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.95,0:03:22.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will I finish composing it before my life runs out?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.55,0:03:28.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you tell me with your Prophecy of Despair?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.72,0:03:32.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really want to hear your dark future?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.57,0:03:39.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorrow makes some songs all the more beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.75,0:03:42.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shrade...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.00,0:03:49.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I finish the song, will you play it with me, my friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.40,0:03:53.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When will High Commander Fudo come back?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.89,0:03:57.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We haven't heard anything from Mikono either.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.34,0:04:00.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please have one, Miss Suomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.67,0:04:03.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, thank you. I avoid high calorie foods late at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.40,0:04:06.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.72,0:04:09.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.75,0:04:12.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fudo will return to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.79,0:04:15.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And he'll bring back the legend of Genesis.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.22,0:04:23.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Girl with hair the color of grass.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.96,0:04:31.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I regret that even though I opened the gate for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.37,0:04:33.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.09,0:04:41.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't forget to keep your promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.46,0:04:48.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What promise? I didn't promise you anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.24,0:04:51.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you don't remember what it was,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.62,0:04:55.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you will keep it for me when the time comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.29,0:05:11.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mix...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.90,0:05:22.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I actually saw her big bangs.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.18,0:05:26.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But they weren't big bangs at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.17,0:05:30.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Andy, what are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.09,0:05:33.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got to sit right here or I'll sink.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.26,0:05:39.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's one of the holes Mix filled.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.26,0:05:45.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep. There are absolutely no weak points in the material she fills with.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.14,0:05:49.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't sink into it even if my power overloads.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.40,0:05:53.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Andy...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.85,0:05:56.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amata...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.65,0:05:59.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say we actually got Mix back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.36,0:06:01.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would I...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.38,0:06:04.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, now that she's a boy,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.51,0:06:07.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,would I still love her the same?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.08,0:06:27.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, well. I didn't smell anyone, but there you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.87,0:06:34.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.62,0:06:36.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you running away from me for?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.05,0:06:44.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're finally one!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.63,0:06:45.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Apollo...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.80,0:06:49.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I am, Apollo..
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.05,0:06:53.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been waiting to see you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.57,0:06:56.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You came for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.03,0:06:58.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikono...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.18,0:07:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wrong, wench.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.00,0:07:02.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're not Apollon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.31,0:07:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're Amagura!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.23,0:07:10.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikono, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.56,0:07:13.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it right there, wench!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.34,0:07:19.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go of her!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.65,0:07:20.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.70,0:07:23.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Join us, wench.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.84,0:07:26.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.92,0:07:29.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amata, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.94,0:07:45.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikono...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.83,0:08:00.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.01,0:08:08.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you clap your hands, what remains between them?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.30,0:08:13.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A right hand and a left. Angel and human.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.45,0:08:16.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man and woman. Plus and minus.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.89,0:08:19.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is in the gap between them?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.73,0:08:26.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's in the gap between my right hand and my left?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.51,0:08:34.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.60,0:08:40.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing there, but it feels warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.86,0:08:46.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haven't I heard this somewhere before?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.20,0:09:01.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Long ago, just after the heavens and earth were separated,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.56,0:09:04.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the world was bathed in a glorious light.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.70,0:09:11.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The flowers sang, while the creatures and insects whispered of love.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.57,0:09:16.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the angels loved, up among the stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.26,0:09:22.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the angels were hunters, and mankind was their prey.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.11,0:09:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In this war, there fought an Angel of Slaughter named Apollonius,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.70,0:09:35.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and he met a girl named Celiane, and they fell in love.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.18,0:09:42.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Apollonius betrayed his kind and joined with the humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.93,0:09:51.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He, the traitor, cast off his wings and gave unto the humans a great weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.85,0:09:56.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He piloted a machine Angel and fought against the angels.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.11,0:10:01.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the legend written in the Book of Genesis.{*}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.06,0:10:04.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that's what really happened 12,000 years ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.67,0:10:05.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.87,0:10:12.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the previous story, the story of 24,000 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.70,0:10:20.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The wheel of Fate has turned again, and the legend is about to be told once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.14,0:10:23.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once more...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.73,0:10:36.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amata Sora! Explain yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.40,0:10:39.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I do not recall ordering a sortie!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.31,0:10:41.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going after Mikono.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.49,0:10:43.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were not given permission to move out!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.84,0:10:45.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's calling me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.81,0:10:47.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikono is calling for help.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.59,0:10:49.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to move fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.90,0:11:01.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikono...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.97,0:11:05.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't let someone I love leave me again...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.73,0:11:14.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, go to the one you love.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.05,0:11:17.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And go also to the Wings of the Sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.45,0:11:23.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you, fragmented one, wake up now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.86,0:11:32.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amata...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.42,0:11:36.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vector Z's transmitter is off. We can't track it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.08,0:11:40.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cayenne, can you see where it is with the Prophecy of Despair?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.84,0:11:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll try.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.23,0:11:59.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.81,0:12:12.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the city where Mikono and I first met.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.10,0:12:19.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened here?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{cm}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.01,0:12:50.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.30,0:12:56.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The gap between light and darkness, as written in the Book of Genesis.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.13,0:13:01.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cockpit's empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.60,0:13:03.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did Amata go?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.31,0:13:07.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The city where Amata and I first met.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.33,0:13:11.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And where we had our first Union.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.54,0:13:21.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.86,0:13:25.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did they all go?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.71,0:13:32.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd heard it was locked down after that fight,{tlnote I think there's something about keeping watch on the town in there but the important thing is everyone was pushed out and the town is off limits}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.37,0:13:34.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I didn't know it was like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.95,0:13:37.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is Mikono here too?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.58,0:13:39.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what my power says.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.95,0:13:44.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you did come after Mikono, Amata...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.89,0:13:47.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's split up and search.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.05,0:13:59.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir?{I guess this is what he called oyajisan}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.38,0:14:29.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are these?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.16,0:14:33.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They aren't mine. Whose are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.97,0:14:37.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What am I supposed to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.25,0:14:41.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did Mikage send me here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.01,0:14:45.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it smells...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.38,0:14:52.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure I was here, a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.14,0:15:16.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amata...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.89,0:15:18.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amata...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.20,0:15:20.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amata...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.98,0:15:44.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've finally unlocked those suppressed memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.42,0:15:51.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Skies of Aquaria"?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.93,0:16:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikono...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.70,0:16:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikono!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.25,0:16:27.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amata!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.59,0:16:30.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zessica? What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.55,0:16:34.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I came to get you, Amata.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.81,0:16:40.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, Chairman Crea ordered us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.06,0:16:41.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me and Cayenne.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.11,0:16:46.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. It's my fault for going against orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.65,0:16:56.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This whole town is locked down, so everyone was evacuated.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.40,0:17:00.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's why there's no one left.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.75,0:17:04.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How come you had to come here so badly? You even disobeyed orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.65,0:17:07.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know... but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.45,0:17:08.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.39,0:17:12.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I felt like Mikono was calling for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.38,0:17:19.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.33,0:17:24.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I have to wait for 12,000 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.60,0:17:34.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amata, you used to work in this theater, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.57,0:17:38.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And this is where you met Mikono?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.33,0:17:39.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zessica?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.43,0:17:43.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amata...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.31,0:17:43.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.60,0:17:50.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After the next 12,000 years... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.69,0:18:03.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is not the place of you humans to write your own false tales.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.45,0:18:08.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not when a true legend is about to come to pass again!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.49,0:18:13.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zessica!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.23,0:18:14.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run! This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.13,0:18:18.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter? Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.03,0:18:32.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run, little beasts of love, run.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.10,0:18:35.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run to the promised land!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.26,0:18:50.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amata!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.52,0:18:54.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zessica!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.00,0:19:00.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zessica!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.75,0:19:04.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.10,0:19:07.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop. I'm not getting out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.08,0:19:08.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.42,0:19:14.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget about me! Just go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.63,0:19:19.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never! I won't leave you behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.55,0:19:21.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amata...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.31,0:19:30.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Amata.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.02,0:19:46.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zessica! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.70,0:19:57.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zessica!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.20,0:20:02.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've been looking for you, Amata!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.52,0:20:21.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're here, Cayenne!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.16,0:20:22.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sazanka!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.64,0:20:24.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vector Y... who's in it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.15,0:20:30.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said when I finished the piece, you would play it with me, my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.56,0:20:33.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut it out! You can't Union in your condition!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.68,0:20:39.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no time for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.34,0:20:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.35,0:20:42.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Risky Union!{Not a fan of this name 捨て身 = risking his life}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.78,0:20:45.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Aquarion!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.85,0:20:51.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shrade, why...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.93,0:20:54.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.33,0:20:57.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is so rotten!{Sazanka rotten blah blah there's definitely a better word to go here}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.68,0:21:01.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aquarion Spada!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.76,0:21:20.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Found you, Amata, you pathetic wimp.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.14,0:21:23.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your... {missing line}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.43,0:21:35.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Wings of the Sun are soon to awaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.27,0:21:38.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to say I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.89,0:21:44.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What I did to you... please, forgive me...{annoying vague shit!}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.45,0:21:49.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You... you saw it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.99,0:21:53.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I didn't think it was real.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.82,0:22:17.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I saw Amata, pathetically unable to do a thing about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.54,0:22:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.48,0:22:27.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.31,0:22:31.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{both}You're me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{ed}
