Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.33,0:24:21.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Loving someone is supposed to be more kind and gentle.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.44,0:24:24.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no!
